description.narrative: There was a timely and continuous supply of essential medicines and vaccines in DPRK, ensuring equitable access to immunization and IMNCI. This included the provision of EMK kits and HHD kits in 50 priority counties, ORS nationwide (excluding Jagang Province), and vaccines and injection devices throughout the country.By June 2020, post Measles Rubella campaign coverage survey was successfully conducted with a national coverage of 99%. National DPT1-DPT3 dropout was reduced to 1%. Zero months of stock outs of ORS reported at national level with 75.5% reported cases of diarrhea receiving ORS. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:28/08/2020
